  icon: {fileID: 8887522133862586935, guid: f4115241b7ab31044a3b978d072f5de6, type: 3}
  fullArt: {fileID: 8887522133862586935, guid: f4115241b7ab31044a3b978d072f5de6, type: 3}
  subtitle: 
  journalDescription: 'Journal Description

    A seed carried from the last clean

    watering
    hole in the savanna.


    Ndugu pressed it into your hand

    without a word.
    No ceremony.

    Just the weight of something

    that still wants to grow.


    Your
    strikes hit harder.

    The land fights back through you.


    EFFECT: +7.5
    melee damage'
